QuestData.Title: Bring the Reinforcements
QuestData.Description: Hey there, Commander. You know, with all of the fighting concentrated here in Tanaan, we've got plenty of extra supplies just sitting around in our nearby outposts.$B$BYou just give me the order and I'll make sure some of them get sent our way!
QuestData.LogDescription: Talk to Fraggs and choose which reinforcements to bring to Tanaan.
